      "instruction": "<p><strong>Preheat</strong> the oven to 230&deg;C/ 210&deg;C (fan)/ 450&deg;F/ Gas 8</p>\r\n<p><strong>Boil</strong> a kettle&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Slice</strong> the squash in half lengthways, remove the seeds (with a spoon) and slice into wedges</p>",
